When you go to edit the IP Address that should be trusted, it's unclear what format to enter the IP addresses in.  Should they be comma delimited? Should there be a newline between them?  If you look at the equivalent field in Jira, the directions say:
{quote}  Incoming requests will only be permitted from hosts whose IP Address is listed (one per line). Use an asterisk \(*\) for wildcard matching.  {quote}

