We would like to publish an RSS feed that includes the titles of recently updated documents, including new email.  The feeds produced by Confluence always include the entire content of email messages.  This is unfortunate and means that we need to somehow filter the feeds locally before presenting them to the end user.

Ideally the "For Pages, show..." section of the feed builder would apply to all document types.

